title: InitializeBACnetSetpointReference (Function)
text:
FUNCTION InitializeBACnetSetpointReference : BOOL
Initializes a IEC_BACNET_SETPOINT_REFERENCE according to a given BACnetSetpointReference struct.

rows.Name: setpointRef
rows.Comment: The BACnetSetpointReference to use for initialization.

rows.Name: bacSetpointRef
rows.Comment: The BACnet set point reference to operate on.
